             were indicted for <rs id="t18290910-276-off1519" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18290910-276-off1519" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290910-276-off1519" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18290910-276-cd1520" type="crimeDate">28th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290910-276-off1519 t18290910-276-cd1520"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 2s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18290910-276-victim2594" type="victimName">
                           Thomas Spooner 
                           Rowsell
                        <interp inst="t18290910-276-victim2594" type="surname" value="Rowsell"></interp>
